# Copy to .env.local if you want to override locally (optional).
#
# Production / Dokploy — expose at `vite build` time (env in Dokploy UI).
# Prefer hostname only so the scheme always matches how users open the site
# (important behind Cloudflare + HTTP origins):
#   VITE_API_HOST=api.predictionking.lukemiller.dev
#
# Optional full-URL override (must match page scheme to avoid mixed content):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.predictionking.lukemiller.dev
#
# Local dev — leave both unset; vite.config.ts proxies /api → http://localhost:5166
